OOC: So much to do soo little time!  Whistler is about 6 feet tall for anyone 
who cares

::Whistler::
    He gulps as the missiles hit him in the chest.  They tore into his chest 
and flung him off to the side bouncing off of the CF's shields.  He was 
barely alive and probably would have died in the huge blast that followed, 
but he had been blasted far away from the battle.
